    "combat1": {
      "name": "Allegoria",
      "description": "Normal Attack\nProclaims a decree in the primordial tongue and performs up to 3 attacks that deal Pyro DMG.\n\nCharged Attack\nConsumes a certain amount of Stamina to deal AoE Pyro DMG to opponents in front of her after a short casting time.\n\nPlunging Attack\nNicole plunges towards the ground from mid-air, damaging all opponents in her path. Also deals AoE Pyro DMG upon impact with the ground.",
      "descriptionRaw": "<color=#FFD780FF>Normal Attack</color>\nProclaims a decree in the primordial tongue and performs up to 3 attacks that deal <color=#FF9999FF>Pyro DMG</color>.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Charged Attack</color>\nConsumes a certain amount of Stamina to deal <color=#FF9999FF>AoE Pyro DMG</color> to opponents in front of her after a short casting time.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Plunging Attack</color>\nNicole plunges towards the ground from mid-air, damaging all opponents in her path. Also deals <color=#FF9999FF>AoE Pyro DMG</color> upon impact with the ground.",
