    "combat2": {
      "name": "Revelation: Uncreated Light",
      "description": "Recreates a fleeting glimpse of an age long past, when the angels acted on the authority of the heavens, bestowing the **Grace of Kenosis****** effect on nearby party members. This increases their ATK and deals AoE Pyro DMG, as well as creates a Shield of Blazing Light.\nThe Shield of Blazing Light's DMG Absorption is based on Nicole's ATK, and it will absorb Pyro DMG at 250% effectiveness.",
      "descriptionRaw": "Recreates a fleeting glimpse of an age long past, when the angels acted on the authority of the heavens, bestowing the {LINK#N11310001}<color=#FFD780FF>Grace of Kenosis</color>{/LINK}{LINK#N11310002}{/LINK} effect on nearby party members. This increases their ATK and deals <color=#FF9999FF>AoE Pyro DMG</color>, as well as creates a Shield of Blazing Light.\nThe Shield of Blazing Light's DMG Absorption is based on Nicole's ATK, and it will absorb <color=#FF9999FF>Pyro DMG</color> at 250% effectiveness.",
