    "passive1": {
      "name": "Methexis",
      "descriptionRaw": "For 20s after unleashing the Elemental Skill <color=#FFD780FF>{LINK#S11312}Revelation: Uncreated Light{/LINK}</color>, Nicole will continuously \"observe\" the other current active party members. After the observed character has remained on the field for 3s, their {LINK#N11310001}<color=#FFD780FF>Grace of Kenosis</color>{/LINK} is upgraded to {LINK#N11310002}<color=#FFD780FF>Guidance of Theosis</color>{/LINK}, increasing their ATK by an additional 300. If the observed character is a Hexerei character, <color=#FFD780FF>Grace of Kenosis</color> is upgraded to <color=#FFD780FF>Guidance of Theosis</color> straight away.\nWhen characters other than Nicole who have <color=#FFD780FF>Guidance of Theosis</color> leave the field, their effect reverts to <color=#FFD780FF>Grace of Kenosis</color>.",
      "description": "For 20s after unleashing the Elemental Skill **Revelation: Uncreated Light**, Nicole will continuously \"observe\" the other current active party members. After the observed character has remained on the field for 3s, their **Grace of Kenosis** is upgraded to **Guidance of Theosis**, increasing their ATK by an additional 300. If the observed character is a Hexerei character, Grace of Kenosis is upgraded to Guidance of Theosis straight away.\nWhen characters other than Nicole who have Guidance of Theosis leave the field, their effect reverts to Grace of Kenosis."
    },
    "passive2": {
      "name": "Philokalia",
      "descriptionRaw": "When Elemental DMG from nearby active party members hits an opponent, Nicole's own {LINK#N11310001}<color=#FFD780FF>Grace of Kenosis</color>{/LINK} effect is upgraded to {LINK#N11310002}<color=#FFD780FF>Guidance of Theosis</color>{/LINK} for 8s.",
      "description": "When Elemental DMG from nearby active party members hits an opponent, Nicole's own **Grace of Kenosis** effect is upgraded to **Guidance of Theosis** for 8s."
    },
    "passive3": {
      "name": "Nepsis",
      "descriptionRaw": "When you are in Teyvat and not in combat, Nicole's Charged Attack becomes \"Emissarial Guidance\" if you have already obtained the current region's Treasure Compass. Emissarial Guidance: Calls upon nearby Seelie to show the way, triggering an effect similar to the region's Treasure Compass.\nThis effect has a cooldown time of 5 seconds and does not work in Domains, Trounce Domains, and the Spiral Abyss.",
      "description": "When you are in Teyvat and not in combat, Nicole's Charged Attack becomes \"Emissarial Guidance\" if you have already obtained the current region's Treasure Compass. Emissarial Guidance: Calls upon nearby Seelie to show the way, triggering an effect similar to the region's Treasure Compass.\nThis effect has a cooldown time of 5 seconds and does not work in Domains, Trounce Domains, and the Spiral Abyss."
    },
    "passive4": {
      "name":"Witch's Eve Rite: Light in the Darkness",
      "descriptionRaw":"After completing <color=#FFD780FF>Witch's Homework: The Role of a Guide...?</color>, Nicole becomes a <color=#FFD780FF>Hexerei</color> character. When the party includes at least 2 Hexerei characters, you gain the <color=#FFD780FF>Hexerei: Secret Rite</color> effect, which enhances Hexerei characters.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Hexerei: Secret Rite</color>\nIncreases the DMG dealt by Hexerei characters' <color=#FFD780FF>Arcane Projections</color> by 300% of Nicole's ATK.",
      "description":"After completing Witch's Homework: The Role of a Guide...?, Nicole becomes a Hexerei character. When the party includes at least 2 Hexerei characters, you gain the Hexerei: Secret Rite effect, which enhances Hexerei characters.\n\nHexerei: Secret Rite\nIncreases the DMG dealt by Hexerei characters' Arcane Projections by 300% of Nicole's ATK."
    },
